">Core Directive</div><p>This is not a rebrand. Compass Roofing has real equity — a recognizable name,
an established color family,
and a real track record in the South Florida market. The opportunity is to make the brand experience reflect the level of professionalism that clients need when making a $15,
000–$80,
000 roofing decision.</p></div><div class="section-head">What We Keep</div><div class="card-grid col3"><div class="card"><h4>Company Name</h4><p>Compass Roofing is strong. Clear,
directional,
roofing-specific. No change needed.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Color Family</h4><p>Blue,
white,
and gray are right for the market. We modernize the treatment,
not the direction.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Local Identity</h4><p>South Florida roofing company. Broward County trusted. That stays front and center.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Service Offering</h4><p>Repair,
replacement,
flat,
coatings,
residential,
commercial. Proven service mix,
kept intact.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Market Position</h4><p>Local contractor with residential and commercial capability. We elevate,
not pivot.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Trust Foundation</h4><p>Reviews,
longevity,
past work. This gets amplified and better displayed,
not erased.</p></div></div><div class="section-head">What We Upgrade</div><div class="card-grid col3"><div class="card"><h4>Logo System</h4><p>Evolve to a geometric,
structural,
versatile mark that works on trucks,
signs,
and screens.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Website Architecture</h4><p>Build a real SEO-ready content structure with service,
location,
and project pages.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Typography</h4><p>Montserrat Bold for display,
Inter for body. Clean,
readable,
modern.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Material Treatment</h4><p>Storm blue glass,
brushed aluminum,
metallic borders — roofing-specific material language.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Conversion System</h4><p>Inspection-first CTAs,
multi-step forms,
sticky mobile call,
lead routing by service type.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Proof Sections</h4><p>Project galleries,
review cards,
local service area maps — all surfaced prominently.</p></div></div></div>< !-- ── 02 POSITIONING ── --><div class="chapter"><div class="chapter-num">02</div><h2>Positioning & Core Idea</h2><div class="chapter-sub">One idea. Every page reinforces it.</div><div class="copy-block"><div class="eyebrow">Primary Brand Idea</div><h3>"Know Where Your Roof Stands." </h3><p>Most homeowners delay roofing decisions because they don't know if they need a $500 repair or a $25,000 replacement. Compass Roofing removes that anxiety with clear inspections, honest recommendations, and a team that explains the real situation before asking for a commitment.</p>
 <div class="btn-primary">Schedule Roof Inspection</div><div class="btn-ghost-light">Explore Services</div></div><div class="section-head">Supporting Lines</div><div class="card-grid col2"><div class="card"><h4>Primary Supporting Line</h4><p>"Clear Direction. Stronger Roofs." — Used in headers,
email signatures,
and truck graphics alongside the primary idea.</p></div><div class="card"><h4>Storm-Ready Variant</h4><p>"Storm-Ready Roofing With Clear Direction." — Used seasonally,
