/><path d="M32 26 L32 38" stroke="#8A8E99" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5" /><path d="M44 18 L44 38" stroke="#8A8E99" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5" /><polygon points="32,10 35,20 32,17 29,20" fill="#D4870A" /><text x="68" y="28" font-family="Montserrat, sans-serif" font-weight="800" font-size="13" fill="#1B3A6B">COMPASS</text><text x="68" y="46" font-family="Montserrat, sans-serif" font-weight="400" font-size="10" fill="#5A5E6B" letter-spacing="1.5">ROOFING</text></svg><div class="logo-concept-label">Concept D</div><div class="logo-concept-name">Standing-Seam Metal Roof</div></div></div><div class="section-head">Logo System Requirements</div><div class="card-grid col2"><div class="card"><h4>Required Versions</h4><ul class="check-list"><li>Primary horizontal logo (mark + wordmark)</li><li>Stacked logo (mark above wordmark)</li><li>Icon-only mark</li><li>Dark background version</li><li>One-color version (all blue, all white)</li><li>Social profile version (square crop, icon mark)</li><li>Truck/signage version (high contrast, bold)</li></ul></div><div class="card"><h4>Application Notes</h4><ul class="check-list"><li>Minimum size: 120px wide on screen,
