use white version with semi-opaque overlay if needed</li><li>Metallic silver treatment available for premium print applications</li></ul></div></div></div>< !-- ── 04 COLOR & MATERIAL ── --><div class="chapter"><div class="chapter-num">04</div><h2>Color & Material System</h2><div class="chapter-sub">Roofing-specific material treatment. Every color decision maps to a real material or condition in the Compass Roofing world.</div><div class="section-head">Primary Palette</div><div class="palette"><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#1B3A6B;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Compass Blue</div><div class="swatch-hex">#1B3A6B</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#2251A3;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Storm Blue</div><div class="swatch-hex">#2251A3</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#4A7CC7;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Sky Blue</div><div class="swatch-hex">#4A7CC7</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#F8F7F4; border:1px solid #E0DDD7;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Warm White</div><div class="swatch-hex">#F8F7F4</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#E8E6E1;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Soft Gray</div><div class="swatch-hex">#E8E6E1</div></div></div><div class="section-head">Secondary & Accent Palette</div><div class="palette"><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#1A1C22;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Storm Charcoal</div><div class="swatch-hex">#1A1C22</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#111318;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Deep Charcoal</div><div class="swatch-hex">#111318</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#8A8E99;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Brushed Silver</div><div class="swatch-hex">#8A8E99</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#C4C8D4;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Metallic Light</div><div class="swatch-hex">#C4C8D4</div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#D4870A;"></div><div class="swatch-label">Signal Amber</div><div class="swatch-hex">#D4870A</div></div></div><div class="section-head">Material Language</div><div class="card-grid col3"><div class="card-dark"><h4>Storm Blue Glass</h4><p>Deep blue-tinted frosted panels. Used for hero overlays,
